{
  "stem": "27285.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't-- somehow I was much more clever than now, I guess, because [LAUGHS] I didn't want to forget the language.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I always read, I always read.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In German, as well, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's how I didn't forget.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from '38-- end of '38, until '42, when we went to the camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of [LAUGHS] the Jewish version of?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Horrible, really horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was-- we were all in one room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, all the boys in one room, all the girls in one room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was from the age of five till 18.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very cramped, it was-- no privacy, of course, no-- there was nothing enjoyable there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the leading lady, Ms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Green, she was called, was really quite a sadist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was very, a very horrible time, and only later, when we already spoke the language, which goes very fast with children, we united against her.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had something in common.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it will sound strange, but the first time I felt again relaxed or happy as a child, was in Terezin, and not in the Jewish orphanage of Brno.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in Terezin-- it's also the external things, of course, but in Terezin, we were all in the same boat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all Jewish, there was no problem anymore of being an orphan, or not knowing the language, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were all thrown together, and we knew we had to stick together, somehow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But going back to the orphanage, it was already more and more those anti-Jewish laws that came into existence in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are not supposed to learn, we are not supposed to go and buy anything, and we couldn't buy anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On top of that we were really hungry in this orphanage.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
